  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink255-kilavi">niṉṉāṟkāṇappaṭṭavaḷ ettaṉmaiyaḷ eṉṟa pāṅkaṟkut talaimakaṉ colliyatu.   </p>
        <p xml:lang="en">
         
What the hero told [his] companion, who asked, “Of what kind is the lady seen by you?”

          
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink255">
<l>kuṉṟak kuṟavaṉ kātaṉ maṭamakaḷ</l>
<l>varaiyara makaḷirp puraiyuñ cāyala</l>
<l>ḷaiya ḷarumpiya mulaiyaḷ</l>
<l>ceyya vāyiṉaṇ mārpiṉaḷ cuṇaṅkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>The beloved, naïve daughter of the hill-dweller</l>
        <l>has an elegance like that of mountain nymphs.</l>
        <l>She is wondrous; she has budding breasts,</l>
        <l>red lips, and beauty spots on her chest.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
